08180595\"></a><span lang=\"EN-AU\">1.1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">CODE OF CONDUCT POLICY</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 20.7px;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">At FNQH Pathology (\"the Company\") we require that all of our employees conduct themselves according to the highest standards of ethics, integrity, and behaviour when dealing with our clients, colleagues and other stakeholders.&nbsp;&nbsp;This includes, but is not necessarily limited to, full compliance with all legal obligations imposed by statute or any other source of law.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">This Code establishes the standards of behaviour that must be met by all employees. Where these standards are not met, appropriate disciplinary action will be taken. In cases where the breach involves serious misconduct, this may result in summary dismissal. In cases where a breach of the policy involves a breach of any law, then the relevant government authorities or the police may be notified.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"_Toc108180596\"></a><span lang=\"EN-AU\">1.1.1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">OPERATION</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">The purpose of this policy is to make it clear what the Company expects from employees, and employees are required to be familiar with and comply with the terms of this policy at all times.&nbsp;&nbsp;Failure to do so may result in disciplinary action, including potentially termination of employment.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">In so far as this policy imposes any obligations on the Company, those obligations are not contractual and do not give rise to any contractual rights. To the extent that this policy describes benefits and entitlements for employees, they are discretionary in nature and are also not intended to be contractual.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">The terms and conditions of employment that are intended to be contractual out in an employee&rsquo;s written employment contract.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">The Company may unilaterally introduce, vary, remove or replace this policy at any time.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"_Toc108180597\"></a><span lang=\"EN-AU\">1.1.2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">STANDARDS OF CONDUCT</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">The standards expected of employees include:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Compliance with all Company and workplace policies, procedures, rules, regulations and contracts;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Compliance with all laws;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Compliance with all reasonable and lawful instructions given by or on behalf of the Company;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoToc2\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Devotion of the employee&rsquo;s entire time, attention and skill during normal working hours and at other times as reasonably necessary for the employee to perform their duties;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To be honest and fair in dealings with customers, clients, co-workers, Company management and the general public, and to treat them with courtesy and respect;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To be faithful and diligent, and actively pursue the Company&rsquo;s best interests at all times;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To work in a safe and compliant manner, and to observe all workplace health and safety rules and responsibilities;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Refraining from any discriminatory, bullying or harassing behaviour toward customers, clients, co-workers, Company management and the general public;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not make any statements to the media about the Company&rsquo;s business, unless expressly authorised to do so by the Company;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not make any statements about the Company on social media, or any other public platform, that may harm the Company&rsquo;s reputation;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not, in connection with the employee&rsquo;s employment, accept any financial or other benefit from any entity other than the Company &ndash; unless acceptance of such benefit is in accordance with the Company&rsquo;s other workplace policies or is otherwise disclosed to the Company and expressly permitted by the Company;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Dependent on terms of the employment contract to determine if you are permitted to engage in any employment or provide any services, thus seeking verification and/or company consent.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Dependent on terms of employment to not engage in any employment or provide any services to a supplier or competitor of the Company, except with the Company&rsquo;s prior written consent;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Immediately disclosing any potential, perceived or actual conflict of interest (whether direct or indirect) that may give rise to a conflict with the performance of the employee&rsquo;s obligations to the Company, or the Company&rsquo;s business, confidential information or reputational interests.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Company may direct employees to take action to eliminate or reduce any such conflict, and employees must comply with such directions;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not engage in conduct, whether during or after work hours, that in the opinion of the Company causes damage or potential damage to the Company&rsquo;s property or reputation;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not use, or come to work while affected by use of prohibited drugs or alcohol;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not discriminate on the basis of personal characteristics including (but not limited to) sex, race, disability, pregnancy, age, marital status or sexual orientation;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To ensure and maintain punctuality;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To respect the Company&rsquo;s property;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To dress in an appropriate manner and to ensure that appearance is presentable, clean, neat and tidy (including but not limited to wearing any uniform that is required of you by the Company);</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not use Company internet to access and/or download sexually explicit material or other offensive material;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To not use Company email to send sexually explicit or&nbsp;&nbsp;suggestive material, or other offensive or harassing material;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">To maintain both during employment and after termination of employment with the Company, the confidentiality of any confidential information, records or other materials acquired during the course of employment;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">At all times, behave in a way that upholds the Company&rsquo;s core values and the integrity and good reputation of the Company;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Reporting any conduct of other workplace participants which is in breach of any of the above, or potentially in breach of any of the above, without delay</span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3><a name=\"_Toc108180598\"></a><span lang=\"EN-AU\">1.1.1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">OTHER POLICIES</span></h3>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">Employees are encouraged to read this policy in conjunction with other relevant Company policies, including:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Workplace Anti-Bullying &amp; Anti-Harassment Policy;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: Symbol;\">&middot;<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Equal Employment Opportunity and Anti-Discrimination Policy.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span><a name=\"_Toc108180599\"></a><a name=\"_Toc43193955\"></a><span lang=\"EN-AU\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">Managing Records kept on the basis of this document</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">All records supporting this policy shall be kept in the FNQH Pathology document management system in the location, or system based, indicated in the procedure document. Any additional or deleted records shall be kept account of in the FNQH Pathology logging system such that any future enquiry will be able to clearly identify when the changes occurred, who made them, what these changes were and how the changes were approved.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt;\"><a name=\"_Toc108180600\"></a><a name=\"_Toc43193956\"></a><a name=\"_Toc42774212\"></a><a name=\"_Toc31271019\"></a><a name=\"_Toc30670090\"></a><span lang=\"EN-AU\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-AU\">Validity and Document Management</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">This document is valid from the date of its approval and will be reviewed on an annual basis. The current working copy will be identified as such, and any superseded documents will be archived and maintained for a period of five years.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-AU\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">New versions will be identified with a versioning number. Full integers will denote a major document version, and a decimal number will indicate minor amendments or edits.</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>',	'FNQH Pathology - Digital first, better patient outcomes',	1,	'FNQH-POL-AD080722 [INTERNAL]',	'',	0,	1,	452,	'2022-09-17 11:48:47');



